main event: A civilian observed an unidentified flying object over Beach Haven, New Jersey on August 17, 1967.
interesting points: The object was described as a large cigar-shaped object with window outlines,It appeared bright white and moved parallel to the earth before shooting straight up into the clouds,The sighting lasted for about 2-3 minutes and was visible in cloudy conditions,Another sighting by the same observer occurred on August 28, 1967, with a similar description but different behavior,No photographs or physical evidence were obtained to substantiate the sighting.
